Title: Stronger Than Bone
Description:
This giant jade tiger pillar doesn't seem to fit in amidst the hozen buildings.

What it does seem is very hard. Very solid.

You know just the person to bring this to.
ObjectivesText: Bring the Jade Tiger Pillar to Jojo Ironbrow in Morning Breeze Village.
RewardText: GOOD! A true challenge. Let us put this pillar to the test!
